Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: As Saskatchewan’s newest and fastest growing city, Warman is boasts a population of over 11,500 residents and a projected five year average growth rate of 11.02%. Located just 10km north of Saskatoon, this former bedroom community continues to be an attractive location for both commercial and residential development.
